                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-2">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-caret-right mr-2"></i>
                            <a href="http://tckh.dhhp.edu.vn/">Tạp chí khoa học</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-2">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-caret-right mr-2"></i>
